About Me

I'm currently a Senior at Stanford University majoring in American Studies with a focus on race, gender and sexuality in American media and entertainment. Additionally, I'm minoring in Creative Writing with an emphasis on screenwriting. My professional experience spans both scripted and unscripted television, working with development teams to create new and exciting content. In my free time, I perfom improv and standup comedy, create sketch vidoes, and write TV pilots. My most recent pilot won Best Comedy Script in the 2019 All Write Now screenwriting competition.
